- Saas is the easy way to write css. We can easily maintain nested css property. The file type is scss.



# In CSS
.categories-container {
  background-color: red;
}

.category-container {
  background-color: blue;
}

.category-body-container {
  background-color: green;
}

# In SASS
.categories-container {
  background-color: red;

		.category-container {
		  background-color: blue;

					.category-body-container {
					  background-color: green;
					}
		}
}



